sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔理啦，我一月去日本都諗住自己一個人去食。<br />\n新宿分店啲位就隱閉，但我到時就方便會去淺草分店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實日本啲餐廳歡唔歡迎毒撚一個去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係遊客，佢理撚得你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0475e3259f6de53be677345dd52f5ffa5a69f45c","tid":15601,"uid":48445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:25:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇任食推介<br />\n<br />\n上年係大阪食過國產牛， 想搵差唔多level<br />\n<br />\n預6000 yen 一位左右</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓上有個係放題12000yen 食山形牛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果個有好幾個價，最貴好似係12000yen<br />\n我諗住食4500或6000yen既"},{"pid":"3f5905af8126023970b343cfbd3ae0a3a33c5381","tid":15601,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T06:18:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>土古里，有山形牛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢間一個人食唔食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔理啦，我一月去日本都諗住自己一個人去食。<br />\n新宿分店啲位就隱閉，但我到時就方便會去淺草分店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實日本啲餐廳歡唔歡迎毒撚一個去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係遊客，佢理撚得你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a886720992a1c05c50a50e24ac0cf875db41c